      <title>Prof. Collin&#39;s Three Laws of Engineering</title>
      <link>//chenbrian.ca/posts/three-laws-of-engineering/</link>
      <pubDate>Thu, 20 Jan 2022 03:26:06 -0500</pubDate>
      <guid>//chenbrian.ca/posts/three-laws-of-engineering/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h1 id=&#34;the-only-three-rules-an-engineer-needs-to-learn-and-remember&#34;&gt;&amp;ldquo;The only three rules an engineer needs to learn and remember&amp;rdquo;&lt;/h1&gt;&#xA;&lt;ol&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;\( F = ma \)&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;You can&amp;rsquo;t push on a rope.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;To get the answer, you must first know the answer&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ol&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA; &lt;img loading=&#34;lazy&#34; src=&#34;img/image_2023-01-26-01-21-34.png&#34; alt=&#34;image_2023-01-26-01-21-34&#34;  /&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;blockquote&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://civmin.utoronto.ca/home/about-us/directory/professors/michael-collins/&#34;&gt;Michael P. Collins&lt;/a&gt;  &lt;sup id=&#34;fnref:1&#34;&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;#fn:1&#34; class=&#34;footnote-ref&#34; role=&#34;doc-noteref&#34;&gt;1&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;/blockquote&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;If I remember anything from my degree it might be the above three laws and the pursuit of &lt;em&gt;elegance&lt;/em&gt; in design &lt;sup id=&#34;fnref:2&#34;&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;#fn:2&#34; class=&#34;footnote-ref&#34; role=&#34;doc-noteref&#34;&gt;2&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://skulepedia.ca/wiki/Three_Rules_of_Engineering&#34;&gt;source&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;footnotes&#34; role=&#34;doc-endnotes&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;hr&gt;&#xA;&lt;ol&gt;&#xA;&lt;li id=&#34;fn:1&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;We were fortunate enough to be the last cohort to take it under Prof. Collins.&amp;#160;&lt;a href=&#34;#fnref:1&#34; class=&#34;footnote-backref&#34; role=&#34;doc-backlink&#34;&gt;&amp;#x21a9;&amp;#xfe0e;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
